name: Hand Signed Book - The Art of Sketch Theatre Volume 1
description:
The Art of Sketch Theatre Volume 1 is an inspiring collection of sketches, finished work and insightful profiles by over 50 professional artists who have participated in the ongoing SketchTheatre.com project.  Featured artists include Aaron Sims, Aimee Kuester, Ana Bagayan, Apricot Mantle, Axel 13, Brandi Milne,Cameron Davis, Charles Hu, Chet Zar, Chris Ryniak, Corey Miller, Gary Baseman, Greg Simkins, Gris Grimly, Jessica Ward, Lola Gil, Luke Chueh, Michael Hussar, Molly Crabapple, Munk One, Ron English, Shawn Barber, Steven Daily, Tara McPherson, Travis Louie and many more.

The Page on Munk One Page will be hand signed.
